                         Set Cond:  S X=X
                       Kill Logic:  K ^XMB(3.7,DA(2),2,DA(1),1,"AC",$E(X,1,1),DA)
                        Kill Cond:  S X=X
                       Whole Kill:  K ^XMB(3.7,DA(2),2,DA(1),1,"AC")
                             X(1):  NETWORK PRIORITY TRANSMISSION?  (3.702,6)  (Subscr 1)  (Len 1)  (forwards)


